text: Květa Hrušková (25 June 1925 - 30 January 2012)Zemřela Květa Hrušková at the website of Czech Table Tennis Association was a female Czech international table tennis player. She won five World Table Tennis Championship medals during the 1949 World Table Tennis Championships and 1951 World Table Tennis Championships. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2012 deaths Category:Czech female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
